nightlife of Singapore.</span>\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item][timeline_item item_number=\"4\" title=\"Day 4: Day to yourself\"]<span class=\"s1\">This city has so many attractions that we have kept this day to yourself. Try some sumptuous local food or visit the National Museum to understand the history of Singapore or Botanical Gardens. Explore Orchard road for fascinating malls and if your budget allow, why not indulge in some world class shopping. </span>We will meet in the evening for the farewell dinner.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item][timeline_item item_number=\"5\" title=\"Day 5:Departure day\"]Time to bid adieu. Check out from hotel and transfer to Changi International Airport\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item]<strong>End of this memorable tour.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/timeline]\";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Terms and Conditions\";s:7:\"content\";s:1323:\"<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Terms and conditions: </b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Total trip cost: 35,000 INR</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">1. To confirm your spot, you can pay a deposit of 7000 INR (this is a non-refundable amount) </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">2. You will have to pay the remaining amount- 28000 INR before 15th June else your seat will be cancelled.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Cancellation policy: </b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol class=\"ol1\">\r\n 	<li class=\"li3\"><span class=\"s2\">7000 INR deposit is non-refundable. </span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li3\"><span class=\"s2\">75% of the remaining amount will be refunded if you cancel your participation before 45 days of the tour date. </span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li3\"><span class=\"s2\">50% of the remaining amount will be refunded if you cancel your participation before 30 days of the tour date. </span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li3\"><span class=\"s2\">25% of the remaining amount will be refunded if you cancel your participation before 15 days of the tour date. </span></li>\r\n 	<li