tle\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"banner_image\";s:58:\"http://roamingclan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/holi.jpg\";s:24:\"is_banner_image_parallax\";s:1:\"1\";s:19:\"banner_image_repeat\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:11:\"banner_mask\";s:0:\"\";}'),(3986,1741,'tour_tabs_meta','a:2:{s:10:\"tour_badge\";s:1:\"2\";s:4:\"tabs\";a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Itinerary\";s:7:\"content\";s:1566:\"[timeline][timeline_item item_number=\"1\" title=\"Day 1\"] Arrive in Rishikesh before noon. Camp checkin and have hot buffet lunch. Spent some free time to explore the area. Later in the evening go to Rishikesh at <b>Parmarth Niketan for Ganga Aarti  followed by Holika Dahan At Laxman Jhulaa Chowk</b>. Dinner and Overnight stay in camp. Relax yourself and  enjoy camp activities and bonfire and have Dinner.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item][timeline_item item_number=\"2\" title=\"Day 2\"] Early Morning wakeup and <strong>Celebrate Holi</strong> in the camp (Play, eat and celebrate). Later in the afternoon <strong>start River Rafting </strong>from Shivpuri down the Ganges to NIM Beach Rishikesh for around 16 kms<strong>.</strong><strong> </strong>Hit some of the most splashing and enjoyable rapids like<strong> Three Blind mice, Cross Fire, Sweet Sixteen, Body Surfing, Return To Sender, Roller Coaster, Tea Off, Golf Course, Club House, Cash Flow, Initiation, Double Trouble And Hilton. </strong>One can try<strong> </strong><strong>Body Surfing </strong>in this section. In the later part, we float across the past temples and ashrams and Ghats enjoying the riverbank life along the holy river.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item][timeline_item item_number=\"3\" title=\"Day 3]\"]Have morning tea. Pack your bags and after breakfast, start for the optional <b>Jungle Trek to the Neer Waterfall</b><b> (4 kms approx both sides) </b>Arrive in Rishikesh. Tour terminates with the flash back memories.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item]<strong>End of this memorable tour.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/timeline]\";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Location\";s:7:\"c