g-even-though-its-raining-and-windy','','','2015-07-16 18:32:23','2015-07-16 18:32:23','',0,'http://adventure-tours.themedelight.com/?post_type=faq&amp;p=31',0,'faq','',0),(251,2,'2015-07-16 19:14:54','2015-07-16 19:14:54','We understand that you may not have a printer handy when you\'re traveling so it is not necessary to have a printed copy. However, we require that you show ID matching your reservation and also the Order # that is immediately emailed to you after you make your reservation.','Should I print a receipt to show the tour guide?','','publish','closed','closed','','should-i-print-a-receipt-to-show-the-tour-guide','','','2015-07-16 19:14:54','2015-07-16 19:14:54','',0,'http://adventure-tours.themedelight.com/?post_type=faq&amp;p=32',0,'faq','',0),(252,2,'2015-07-16 19:55:04','2015-07-16 19:55:04','Please contact us to get the latest information on your desired trip.','How much does it cost to do a private tour?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-much-does-it-cost-to-do-a-private-tour','','','2015-07-16 19:55:04','2015-07-16 19:55:04','',0,'http://adventure-tours.themedelight.com/?post_type=faq&amp;p=34',0,'faq','',0),(253,2,'2015-07-16 20:14:28','2015-07-16 20:14:28','Yes. Reservations are required for guaranteed spots on all tours. Reservations help us determine the number of guides we need to ensure that our groups remain manageable and enjoyable, and they allow us to notify you of changes to the tour due to weather or anything that could disturb the tours.','Do I have to make a reservation or can I just show up?','','publish','closed','closed','','do-i-have-to-make-a-reservation-or-can-i-just-show-up','','','2015-07-16 20:14:28','2015-07-16 20:14:28','',0,'http://adventure-tours.themedelight.com/?post_type=faq&amp;p=36',0,'faq','',0),(254,2,'2015-07-16 20:30:52','2015-07-16 20:30:52','Wear whatever is comfortable. It is recommended to have a sturdy pair of broken-in trail shoes, boots, or sneakers. It is preferable to dress in layers and wear clo