,(2013,1,'2017-05-20 18:21:11','2017-05-20 18:21:11','<span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Captivating culture and enchanting beaches are yours to enjoy during your trip to the tropical island: Bali, custom tailored to the solo travel experience. Meet like-minded explorers eager to uncover the historical temples erected on the edge of breathtaking cliffs.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Visit the remote, small and stunning Gili Islands where automobiles and motorised traffic is prohibited. The Gili islands are a fantastic destination for divers both novice and scuba savvy.</span>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered tours-tabs__table\" style=\"height: 233px; width: 860px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>Start &amp; end location:</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Ngurah Rai International Airport, Depansar, Bali</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>Trip dates:</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">19th August to 26th August</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>Duration:</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">8 Days</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>Group size:</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">4 to 15</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetic